},{"label":"Microwave"},{"label":"Ice Maker"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"Refrigerator"},{"label":"Freezer"},{"label":"Solar Panels"},{"label":"Water Maker"},{"label":"Wine fridge"},{"label":"Autopilot"},{"label":"Chart Plotter"},{"label":"Radar"},{"label":"VHF handset"}],"toys":[{"label":"Stand up Paddle","quantity":"2"}],"entertainment":["43\" TV","Blue Ray","Bose home cinema 5.1"],"tenders":["50HP RIB"]},"crew":[{"name":"Piotr Treliński","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::aff13b50-7efa-11ee-9a40-e749ad45577e::assets::251c8b60-693b-11f0-a563-3107f99b530d/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Skipper with practical experience in the yachting industry. Currently working as booking manager for Wave Charter in\nSardinia and skipper/caretaker of a Wave 50 catamaran. Co-founder of “Sailing Delight” community and charter agency.\nPreviously involved in launching a 5-catamaran charter base. Focused on growing towards yacht ownership and base\nmanagement.\n\nQUALIFICATIONS\nYacht Skipper - PYA\nMotorboat Skipper - PYA\nShort Range Certificate - RYA\nSTCW - Gdynia\nENG1 - Gdynia\n\nLANGUAGES\nPOLISH - NATIVE\nENGLISH - FLUENT\nSPANISH - BEGINNER+\nFRENCH - BEGINNER\n\nYACHTS\n• 10 000 natucal miles sailed\n• Monohulls up to 54ft\n• Catamarans up to 59ft\n• Captain of privately owned yacht\n• Crewed charters with hostess/cook\n• bareboat charters\n• Worked in fleet charters(12 catamarans)\n\nWORK EXPERIENCE\n2025\nWave Charter Company - Booking manager\nWave 50 - Skipper (Sardinia)\n\n2024\nOceanis 54 Skipper - Private Owner (8 months) 2024\n5400nm Wave 60 Delivery - Italy - Dominican Republic\nLagoon 46 Delivery - Les Sables D’olonne - Majorca\n\n2021 - 2023\nSailing Delight\nBaltic, Croatia, Caribbean\nSea You\nSeychelles, Thailand, Croatia, Greece\nCavo Yachting\nGreece\n\n\n\n\n"},{"name":"Adriana Adamenko","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::aff13b50-7efa-11ee-9a40-e749ad45577e::assets::6649b9a0-693b-11f0-a563-3107f99b530d/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"With over 10 years of experience in gastronomy, I progressed from dining room support to head of bar. Driven by a passion for hospitality and the sea, I transitioned into the yachting industry. Today, I work as a professional yacht hostess, hold a\nskipper’s licence, and continue to build my career in international yachting.\n\nSkills\n• Yacht Skipper\n• Bartending\n• Cooking\n• Deckhand\n• Cleaning\n• High efficiency and organization\n• Keeping order at workplace\n• Good manners\n• English B2\n\nCourses\n• Yacht Skipper PYA\n• STCW\n• ENG1\n• Hospitality Training\n• Foodpairing\n• Chapagne and Wine Sommelier\n• High-proof alcohol courses\n\nWork Experience\n2025 - Wave Charter\nHostess/Deckhandv (permanent crew) on a Wave 50 catamaran in Sardinia\nAnd additional charters in Saba 50 from the same fleet.\n\n2025 - Samana Yachts\nHostess/Deckhand - Worked on day charters for premium customers and investors for Samana Group in Dominican Republic.\n\n2024-2025 - Wave 60\nDelivery - Deckhand - 5400 nautical miles in delivery from Chiavari, crossing the Atlantic to Dominican Republic.\n\n2024 - Oceanis 54\nHostess/Deckhand  - 6 months season on private yacht in Corsica.\n\n2024 - Lagoon 46\nDelivery - Deckhand - Winter delivery from Sables D’olonne to Majorca\n\n2023– 2024 - Pod Gigantami\nBartender - Restaurant opened by renowned journalist Piotr Kędzierski, specializing in traditional Polish dishes presented in a modern style. On weekends, the restaurant hosts high-class events until the early morning hours, featuring excellent DJs.\n\n2019 – 2021 - Woda Ognista\n50 best discovery by 50 Best Bars & Restaurants\nBar’s Manager - One of the best Polish cocktail bars, where each cocktail menu is inspired by the interwar period and based on Polish seasonal ingredients.\n\n\n"}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":950000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":950000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":1720000,"displayCurrency